In Europe, the emphasis is shifting towards sustainability and eco-friendly technologies. The European Union's stringent regulations on emissions have prompted manufacturers to develop greener coupling systems. Reports showed a 15% growth in eco-friendly coupling solutions from 2021 to 2022, reflecting the urgency to meet sustainability goals.

